#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:62
msgid ""
"Notice how the inputs for the :guilabel:`Warehouse` field, for both the Odoo "
"configuration and the Sendcloud configuration, are the exact same."
msgstr ""
"ध्यान दें कि Odoo कॉन्फ़िगरेशन और SendCloud कॉन्फ़िगरेशन दोनों के "
"लिए :guilabel:`वेयरहाउस` फ़ीलड के इनपुट बिलकुल समान हैं।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:66
msgid "Generate Sendcloud credentials"
msgstr "SendCloud क्रेडेंशियल जनरेट करें"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the Sendcloud account, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Integrations` in the menu on the right. Next, search for :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Native`. Then, click on :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"SendCloud अकाउंट में, दाईं ओर मेन्यू में :menuselection:`सेटिंग --> इंटिग्रेशन` पर नेविगेट "
"करें। अगला, :guilabel:`Odoo Native` खोजें। फिर, :guilabel:`कनेक्ट करें` पर क्लिक करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:71
msgid ""
"After clicking on :guilabel:`Connect`, the page redirects to "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud API` settings page, where the :guilabel:`Public and "
"Secret Keys` are produced. The next step is to name "
"the :guilabel:`Integration`. The naming convention is as follows: `Odoo "
"CompanyName`, with the user's company name replacing `CompanyName` (e.g. "
"`Odoo StealthyWood`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`कनेक्ट करें` पर क्लिक करने के बाद, पेज :guilabel:`SendCloud एपीआई` सेटिंग "
"पेज पर रीडायरेक्ट हो जाता है, जहां :guilabel:`पब्लिक और सीक्रेट कीज़` उत्पन्न होती हैं। "
"अगला चरण :guilabel:`इंटिग्रेशन` को नाम देना है। नामकरण परंपरा इस प्रकार है: `Odoo "
"CompanyName`, जिसमें उपयोगकर्ता की कंपनी का नाम `CompanyName` को बदल देता है (जैसे "
"`Odoo StealthyWood`)।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:76
msgid ""
"Then, check the box next to :guilabel:`Service Points` and select the "
"shipping services for this integration. After saving, the :guilabel:`Public "
"and Secret Keys` are generated."
msgstr ""
"फिर, :guilabel:`सर्विस पॉइंट` के बगल में बॉक्स को चेक करें और इस इंटिग्रेशन के लिए शिपिंग "
"सर्विस चुनें। सेव करने के बाद, :guilabel:`पब्लिक और सीक्रेट कीज़` जनरेट हो जाती हैं।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Configuring the Sendcloud integration and receiving the credentials."
msgstr "SendCloud इंटिग्रेशन को कॉन्फ़िगर करना और क्रेडेंशियल प्राप्त करना।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:86
msgid ""
"To ensure seamless Sendcloud integration with Odoo, :ref:`install <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` and :ref:`link <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` the Sendcloud shipping connector "
"to the Sendcloud account. Then, :ref:`configure Odoo fields <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, so Sendcloud can accurately "
"pull shipping data to generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Odoo के साथ निर्बाध SendCloud इंटिग्रेशन सुनिश्चित करने के लिए, SendCloud शिपिंग कनेक्टर "
"को :ref:`इंस्टॉल <inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` करें और "
"SendCloud अकाउंट से :ref:`लिंक <inventory/shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-"
"module>` करें। फिर, :ref:`Odoo फ़ीलड को कॉन्फ़िगर करें <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, ताकि SendCloud लेबल जनरेट करने के "
"लिए शिपिंग डेटा को सटीक रूप से प्राप्त कर सके।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:94
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable pickup points on websites <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-pickups>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`वेबसाइटों पर पिकअप पॉइंट सक्षम करें <inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-"
"pickups>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:99
msgid "Install Sendcloud shipping module"
msgstr "SendCloud शिपिंग मॉड्यूल इंस्टॉल करें"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:101
msgid ""
"After the Sendcloud account is set up and configured, it's time to configure "
"the Odoo database. To get started, go to Odoo's :guilabel:`Apps` module, "
"search for the `Sendcloud Shipping` integration, and install it."
msgstr ""
"SendCloud अकाउंट सेट अप और कॉन्फ़िगर हो जाने के बाद, Odoo डेटाबेस को कॉन्फ़िगर करने का "
"समय आ गया है। शुरू करने के लिए, Odoo के :guilabel:`ऐप्लिकेशन` मॉड्यूल में जाएं, "
"`Sendcloud Shipping` इंटिग्रेशन खोजें और इसे इंस्टॉल करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Sendcloud Shipping module in the Odoo Apps module."
msgstr "Odoo ऐप्लिकेशन मॉड्यूल में SendCloud शिपिंग मॉड्यूल।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:112
msgid "Sendcloud shipping connector configuration"
msgstr "SendCloud शिपिंग कनेक्टर कॉन्फ़िगरेशन"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:114
msgid ""
"Once installed, activate the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping` module "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"The :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector` setting is found under "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Connectors` section."
msgstr ""
"इंस्टॉल हो जाने के बाद, :menuselection:`इन्वेंटरी --> कॉन्फ़िगरेशन --> सेटिंग` "
"में :guilabel:`SendCloud शिपिंग` मॉड्यूल को सक्रिय करें। :guilabel:`SendCloud कनेक्टर` "
"सेटिंग :guilabel:`शिपिंग कनेक्टर` सेक्शन के अंतर्गत पाई जाती है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"After activating the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector`, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Shipping Methods` page, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SendCloud कनेक्टर` को सक्रिय करने के बाद, सूचीबद्ध कनेक्टर के "
"नीचे :guilabel:`SendCloud शिपिंग मेथड` लिंक पर क्लिक करें। :guilabel:`शिपिंग मेथड` पेज "
"पर पहुंचने के बाद, :guilabel:`नया` पर क्लिक करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Methods` can also be accessed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Shipping "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`शिपिंग मेथड` को :menuselection:`इन्वेंटरी --> कॉन्फ़िगरेशन --> डिलीवरी --"
"> शिपिंग मेथड` पर जाकर भी एक्सेस किया जा सकता है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:126
msgid ""
"Fill out the following fields in the :guilabel:`New Shipping Method` form:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`नया शिपिंग मेथड` फ़ॉर्म में निम्नलिखित फ़ीलड भरें:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: type `Sendcloud DPD`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`शिपिंग मेथड`: `Sendcloud DPD` टाइप करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Sendcloud` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ":guilabel:`प्रोवाइडर`: ड्रॉप-डाउन मेन्यू से :guilabel:`SendCloud` सेलेक्ट करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: set the product that was configured for this "
"shipping method or create a new product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`डिलीवरी प्रॉडक्ट`: वह प्रॉडक्ट सेट करें जो इस शिपिंग मेथड के लिए कॉन्फ़िगर "
"किया गया था या नया प्रॉडक्ट बनाएं।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:132
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Public Key`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SendCloud कॉन्फ़िगरेशन` टैब में, :guilabel:`SendCloud पब्लिक की` एंटर करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:133
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Secret Key`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SendCloud कॉन्फ़िगरेशन` टैब में, :guilabel:`SendCloud सीक्रेट की` एंटर करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:138
msgid "Pickup points"
msgstr "पिकअप पॉइंट"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:140
msgid ""
"Sendcloud's `service point delivery <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/360026097951-FAQ-Service-Points>`_ lets customers choose a pickup "
"location (such as a nearby shop or locker) instead of entering a private "
"delivery address."
msgstr ""
"SendCloud की `सर्विस पॉइंट डिलीवरी <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/360026097951-FAQ-Service-Points>`_ ग्राहकों को प्राइवेट डिलीवरी पते की "
"जगह पिकअप जगह (जैसे कि पास की दुकान या लॉकर) चुनने देती है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:145
msgid ""
"To enable the feature, go to the shipping method form, and in "
"the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, under the :guilabel:`Options` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud Locations` feature."
msgstr ""
"इस फ़ीचर को एनेबल करने के लिए, शिपिंग मेथड फ़ॉर्म पर जाएं, और :guilabel:`SendCloud "
"कॉन्फ़िगरेशन` टैब में, :guilabel:`ऑप्शन` सेक्शन के तहत, :guilabel:`SendCloud लोकेशन का "
"इस्तेमाल करें` फ़ीचर एनेबल करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:150
msgid ""
"Pickup point selection is only available through the **Website** app (the "
"online checkout view). It is not currently possible to select a pickup point "
"manually through the **Sales** app (the internal database view)."
msgstr ""
"पिकअप पॉइंट सेलेक्शन सिर्फ़ **वेबसाइट** ऐप्लिकेशन (ऑनलाइन चेकआउट व्यू) के ज़रिए उपलब्ध है। "
"फ़िलहाल **सेल्स** ऐप्लिकेशन (इंटरनल डेटाबेस व्यू) के ज़रिए मैन्युअली पिकअप पॉइंट सेलेक्ट करना "
"संभव नहीं है।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:154
msgid ""
"For example, if the customer selects a shipping method like *Sendcloud "
"Mondial Relay*, they must choose a pickup point during the checkout process "
"on the website. If no pickup point is selected, the delivery order cannot be "
"validated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"उदाहरण के लिए, अगर ग्राहक *SendCloud Mondial Relay* जैसी शिपिंग मेथड सेलेक्ट करता है, "
"तो उन्हें वेबसाइट पर चेकआउट प्रोसेस के दौरान पिकअप पॉइंट चुनना होगा। अगर कोई पिकअप "
"पॉइंट सेलेक्ट नहीं किया गया है, तो Odoo में डिलीवरी ऑर्डर वैलिडेट नहीं किया जा सकता।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:159
msgid "Load shipping products"
msgstr "शिपिंग प्रॉडक्ट लोड करें"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:161
msgid ""
"After configuring and saving the form, follow these steps to load the "
"shipping products:"
msgstr ""
"फ़ॉर्म को कॉन्फ़िगर और सेव करने के बाद, शिपिंग प्रॉडक्ट लोड करने के लिए ये स्टेप फ़ॉलो करें:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab of the :guilabel:`New "
"Shipping Method` form, click on the :guilabel:`Load your SendCloud shipping "
"products` link."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SendCloud कॉन्फ़िगरेशन` टैब में :guilabel:`नया शिपिंग मेथड` फ़ॉर्म "
"के, :guilabel:`अपने SendCloud शिपिंग प्रॉडक्ट लोड करें` लिंक पर क्लिक करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:165
msgid ""
"Select the shipping products the company would like to use for deliveries "
"and returns."
msgstr ""
"वे शिपिंग प्रॉडक्ट सेलेक्ट करें जिन्हें कंपनी डिलीवरी और रिटर्न के लिए इस्तेमाल करना चाहेगी।"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:166
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`सेलेक्ट` पर क्लिक करें।"

